---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Offline FileSecure Privacy Policy | DK App Tools"
  description="Privacy Policy for Offline FileSecure by DK App Tools."
>
  <section class="section">
    <p class="eyebrow">Privacy Policy</p>
    <h1>Offline FileSecure Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="lead">Last updated: June 15, 2026</p>
    <h2>Overview</h2>
    <p>
      Offline FileSecure is designed as a local-first Android file vault. The app does
      not require an account and does not upload your vault files to DK App Tools servers.
    </p>
    <h2>Data storage</h2>
    <p>
      Files added to the vault are stored locally on your device in encrypted form.
      App settings, PIN-derived access data, recovery data, and temporary preview or
      export files are also handled locally on your device.
    </p>
    <h2>No ads or tracking</h2>
    <p>
      Offline FileSecure does not contain ads, analytics SDKs, tracking SDKs, or server
      sync features.
    </p>
    <h2>Biometric unlock</h2>
    <p>
      If biometric unlock is enabled, authentication is handled by your device. Offline
      FileSecure does not collect or store biometric data.
    </p>
    <h2>Import and export</h2>
    <p>
      Import creates an encrypted copy inside the app. Your original file remains in
      its original location unless you delete it yourself. Export creates a decrypted
      copy at the location you choose.
    </p>
    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>
      For privacy questions, contact DK App Tools at
      <a href="mailto:dkapps.support@proton.me">dkapps.support@proton.me</a>.
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
